data.description: HOME WARRANTY AND OWNER FINANCING OPTIONS AVAILABLE! Stunning new build 4 Bdr Mountain Modern Home with Quandary Peak Views, river access and walking distance to the Lodge by the Blue. The main level floor plan boasts an expansive open space with a large viewing deck and an appointed deck for a hot tub or quiet oasis. There are 2 primary suites - 1 above the garage for added privacy and a large walk-out basement that can be used for an recreation area or additional living spaces.
